    },
    {
      line: "Our agency content estate is fragmented across program offices and there's no single source of truth.",
      body: "Cross-register, strategic. Common in large civilian agencies and defense system commands. Multiple program offices each maintain parallel publishing chains; consolidation requires both target architecture and migration program design before any conversion runs.",
    },
  ]}
